videos.description: Javin DeLaurier gets physical on the steal and takes it in for the two-handed jam for Duke.
videos.headline: DeLaurier steal leads to big jam

videos.description: Marques Bolden gets a big block on Furman's Clay Mounce that leads to a quick 3-pointer from Gary Trent Jr.
videos.headline: Duke block sets up fast-break 3

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. shows off his balance while catching the ball on the run and going up strong for the dunk.
videos.headline: Carter Jr. catches and dunks in traffic

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets free with the spin and finishes with the left-handed hook for Duke.
videos.headline: Bagley spins for the hook shot

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III loses his man with a quick spin and a big two-handed jam for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Bagley twirls around defender for dunk

videos.description: Javin DeLaurier spikes the layup attempt like a volleyball at the end of the first half for Duke.
videos.headline: DeLaurier shuts down Mounce with huge block

videos.description: Marvin Bagley misses the lay-in and gets his rebound for the putback dunk.
videos.headline: Bagley gathers his miss for putback
